sql_query: SELECT main_app_feast.id, main_app_feast.date_created, main_app_feast.date_updated, main_app_feast.created_by_id, main_app_feast.last_updated_by_id, main_app_feast.name, main_app_feast.description, main_app_feast.feast_code, main_app_feast.notes, main_app_feast.month, main_app_feast.day, main_app_feast.prefix FROM main_app_feast WHERE main_app_feast.month = 11 ORDER BY LOWER(main_app_feast.name) ASC;
natural_language_inputs: Show me all the Feasts in the month of 'November', sorted by feast name.
